- `Header1` - Standard navigation header
- `Footer1` - Standard site footer
- `Section` - Base section wrapper (no number, it's a utility)
- `Hero1` - Centered hero section
- `Feature1` - Card grid section
- `Stats1` - Statistics grid
- `Team1` - Team member grid
- `Layout1` - Two-column content + media
- `CTA1` - Centered call-to-action
